(144, 'TableMenu', NULL, 'Dinner menu', '<p><strong>APPETIZERS</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Les Classiques…</p>\r\n<p>Crab meat and avocado salad served in a crispy shell 26 €<br />Duck foie gras, with grison beef served with spicy pear and wine juice 24 €<br />Sea scallops carpaccio, green peas and French caviar 26 €<br />Grilled and preserved vegetables with a Burrata cream 22 €<br />Smoked marinated Gamberronies and Angus beef served like maki 24 €</p>\r\n<p>Les Créations…</p>\r\n<p>Sea urchin with crispy cream, cauliflower and french caviar 31 €<br />Ceviche of Mahi-Mahi, yusu flavoured and beetroot mousseline 22 €<br />Sautéed squid and shrimp flavour with delfino coriander 27 €<br />Poached foie gras, banana and ginger consommé 27 €</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Oscietra caviar 10g/110 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>FISH</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Eaux Chaudes …</p>\r\n<p>Fresh grilled Caribbean lobster, from our aquarium 100g/10 €<br />Lobster gratin 100g/10 €<br />Conch served with a potato and carrot stew 30 €<br />Roasted yellow tail snapper served with leeks fondant 35 €</p>\r\n<p>Eaux Froides … </p>\r\n<p>Monkfish curry tempura, peas mousseline and gravy 36 €<br />Grilled filet of turbot, eggplant caviar and tomato tartare 38 €<br />Maine lobster cannelloni flavoured with tarragon and wild mushrooms 40 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>MEAT</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Les Blanches…</p>\r\n<p>Veal chop spiked with truffles, on parsnip cream 43 €<br />Rack of suckling pig roasted served with cannellonis gratiné 38 €</p>\r\n<p>Les Rouges…</p>\r\n<p>Pyrenean rack of lamb in a clay crust with thyme, panisse and tomato chutney 38 €<br />Pan seared Kobe beef served with potatoes three ways 41 €<br />Instantly smoked squab, the leg comfit with herbs and pearl onions 38 €</p>\r\n<p>Le Vert…</p>\r\n<p>Carrot ravioli glazed with ginger 23 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>DESSERTS / DESERTS</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Iced</p>\r\n<p>A la Carte home-made ice creams and sorbets 16 €</p>\r\n<p>Cold</p>\r\n<p>Chocolate “baba” flambé, at table 18 €<br />Red berries gaspacho, pistachio iced mousse 17 €<br />Meringue and lemon tart, 2011 version 16 €</p>\r\n<p>Warm</p>\r\n<p>Souffléed tart of raspberry and dark chocolate, served with balsamic sauce 18 €<br />Fine pistachio ravioli with a chocolate heart, pear and vanilla soup 17 €<br />Traditional Crêpe Suzette 20 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>LES INCONTOURNABLES</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Parmesan spaghetti &amp; black truffles : appetizer 25 € / main course 38 €<br />Fresh grilled Caribbean lobster, from our aquarium 100g/10 €<br />Lobster gratin 100g/10 €</p>\r\n', NULL, 'gaiac-le-restaurant-dinner-menu', 'Dinner Menu - Le Gaiac', 'Dinner Menu at restaurant Le Gaiac (Hotel Le Toiny Saint-Barthélemy). Chef Stéphane Mazières.', '', '2011-02-28 00:00:00', 1, 0, 0, NULL, 'jean-françois Tricot', 0, NULL, 25, 24, 58, NULL, NULL, '2011-02-28 13:53:49', '2011-02-28 14:18:56', 1),
(145, 'TableMenu', NULL, 'La carte du dîner', '<p><strong><br /><br />ENTRÉES</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Fondant d’Aubergine et Poivrons aux épices Caraïbe 16,00 €<br />Foie gras au Raisiné Condimenté 24,00 €<br />Assiette Christopher : Accras de Langouste et Lambi, Poissons des Iles fumés 25,00 €<br />Risotto de Crevettes au lait de coco et Gingembre 23,00 € <br />Salade de Langouste, marmelade de Mangue et Maracuja 25,00 €<br />Crème de Fruit à Pain, Noisettes torréfiées 16,00 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>PLATS PRINCIPAUX</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Mi-cuit de Thon au lait de Coco, Salade d’Agrumes au Gingembre 26,00 €<br />Filet de Boeuf « Black Angus », Gratin de Christophines 34,00 € <br />Carré d’Agneau rôti, Caviar d’Aubergine au Cumin et Ail Confit 29,00 €<br />Filet de Vivaneau à la Plancha, Cannelloni de Légumes, Emulsion de Crustacés et Passion 29,00 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>DESSERTS </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Moelleux au Chocolat Noir intense, sorbet Coco 12,00 €<br />Crumble aux Pommes, Glace Vanille 12,00 €<br />Panacotta au Lait de coco, Compote de Fruits Exotiques, Sorbet Ananas 12,00 €</p>', NULL, 'taino-le-restaurant-hotel-christopher-la-carte-du-diner', 'Carte du dîner - Le Taïno', 'Carte du dîner au restaurant Le Taïno (Hotel Christopher).', '', '2011-02-28 04:30:00', 1, 0, 0, NULL, 'jean-françois Tricot', 0, NULL, 25, 55, 58, NULL, NULL, '2011-02-28 14:33:33', '2011-02-28 14:37:55', 1),
(146, 'TableMenu', NULL, 'Dinner menu', '<p><strong><br /><br />SALADS</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Hearts of Romaine, Olive Oil, Vinegar, or Mustard Vinaigrette, herbs 10,00 €<br />Tomato Mozzarella, Basil, Sea Salt, Virgin Olive Oil 20,00 €<br />Niçoise Tuna Salad, Green Beans, Egg, Anchovies, Olives 19,00 €<br />Caesar Salad with Anchovy, Boiled Eggs, Garlic Croutons &amp; Reggiano Parmesan Shavings 16,00 €<br />Caesar Salad with BBQ Tiger Shrimps 25,00 €<br />Caesar Salad With Grilled Chicken 18,00 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>COLD STARTERS</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Jumbo Shrimp, Lime Cocktail Sauce 28,00 €<br />Tomato Gazpacho 9,00 €<br />Lobster Cocktail, Mango Pico de Gallo 22,00 €<br />Homemade Smoked Local Fish, Sour Cream 20,00 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>HOT STARTERS</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Sweet Potato Fish Cakes 12,00 €<br />Fish Fritters, Tamarin Sweet and Sour Sauce 17,00 €<br />Conch Fritters Lime and roasted Garlic Mayonnaise 16,00 €<br />Penne Rigate with Grilled Chicken, Pesto &amp; Grilled Pine Nuts 18,00 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>GRILL</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Grilled Filet of Red Snapper, Vegetable Slaw 23,00 €<br />Mahi Mahi Steaks, Corriander beurre Maitre d’Hotel, Breadfruit Chips 21,00 €<br />King Prawns, Roast Pineapple, BBQ Sauce 28,00 €<br />Grilled Lobster 400gr 35,00 €<br />Grilled Lobster 600gr 50,00 €<br />Grilled Beef Shortribs, Crushed Potatoes, Red Wine Jus 22,00 €<br />Grilled Striploin of Beef, Salt Baked Jacket Potatoes, Sour Cream, Bacon, Onion, Cheddar Cheese 23,00 €<br />Caribe Beer Battered Fried Chicken, Grilled Sweet Potatoes 21,00 €<br />Grilled Flank Steak, French Fries, or Green Beans, Herb Butter 22,00 €</p>\r\n<p><strong>ACCOMPAGNEMENTS AU CHOIX / VEGETABLE SIDE ORDERS</strong> (8,00 €)<br />Ratatouille, Riz Créole, Fries; <br />Christophines, Haricots Verts, Pommes de terre en robe des champs (Jacket Potatoes, Sour Cream, Bacon, Onion, Cheddar Cheese), <br />Breadfruit Chips<br />Whipped Potatoes, Garlic Parsley Oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>SANDWICHES</stro