(69, 30, 'en', '<p>We also publish an <a href="http://hello-stbarth.com/hello-stbarth_restaurant-guide_2010_2011.html">annual Saint-barths restaurants, snacks and caterers guide</a>, a free guide you can find at your hotel, your villa, your villa rental agency, in your favorite restaurants or at the Tourism Committee in Gustavia (tourism office).</p>\r\n<p><br />This pratical guide also contains a usefull pull-out restaurant map.</p>\r\n<p><br /><br />Here is an online readable issue</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div><object style="width: 600px; height: 450px;"><param name="movie" value="http://static.issuu.com/webembed/viewers/style1/v1/IssuuViewer.swf?mode=embed&amp;layout=http%3A%2F%2Fskin.issuu.com%2Fv%2Flight%2Flayout.xml&amp;showFlipBtn=true&amp;documentId=101125032915-2b985c7175894b90b8cba320251c5ce9&amp;docName=hello-stbarth_restaurant-guide_2010-2011-full&amp;username=joufdesign&amp;loadingInfoText=Hello-StBath%20Restaurant%20Guide%202010-2011&amp;et=1294327129249&amp;er=69" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="menu" value="false" /><embed src="http://static.issuu.com/webembed/viewers/style1/v1/IssuuViewer.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" style="width: 840px; height: 730px;" flashvars="mode=embed&amp;layout=http%3A%2F%2Fskin.issuu.com%2Fv%2Fcolor%2Flayout.xml&amp;backgroundColor=000000&amp;showFlipBtn=true&amp;documentId=101125032915-2b985c7175894b90b8cba320251c5ce9&amp;docName=hello-stbarth_restaurant-guide_2010-2011-full&amp;username=joufdesign&amp;loadingInfoText=Hello-StBath%20Restaurant%20Guide%202010-2011&amp;et=1294327129249&amp;er=69" /></object>\r\n<div style="width: 600px; text-align: left;">\r\n\r\n<a href="http://hello-stbarth.com/hello-stbarth_restaurant-guide_2010_2011.html" target="_blank">open publication on Hello-StBarth.com</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Restaurants, snacks and carterers free paper guide', 'restaurants-paper-guide', '', 'restaurants-paper-guide', 'Hellolidays laso publish a St. Barts re